ap. [Enlarge image]","key":"fig-bor-out","order":{"number":20,"section":[1,8,0,0,0,0,0]}},{"caption":"Adding a basemap layer. [Enlarge image]","key":"fig-hot-crime","order":{"number":18,"section":[1,7,0,0,0,0,0]}},{"caption":"Only crime classified as anti-social behaviour is shown. [Enlarge image]","key":"fig-one-crime","order":{"number":17,"section":[1,7,0,0,0,0,0]}},{"caption":"Adding a basemap layer. [Enlarge image]","key":"fig-adding-basemap","order":{"number":15,"section":[1,7,0,0,0,0,0]}},{"caption":"Selecting and exporting the crimes that fall within the boroughs of Camden and Islington. [Enlarge image]","key":"fig-select-crimes","order":{"number":13,"section":[1,6,0,0,0,0,0]}},{"caption":"Saving your QGIS project. [Enlarge image]","key":"fig-save-project","order":{"number":8,"section":[1,3,0,0,0,0,0]}},{"caption":"Open QGIS Desktop 3.28. [Enlarge image]","key":"fig-open-qgis","order":{"number":1,"section":[1,1,0,0,0,0,0]}},{"caption":"Inspecting our crime data csv. [Enlarge image]","key":"fig-inspect-data","order":{"number":9,"section":[1,4,0,0,0,0,0]}},{"caption":"Adding vector data. [Enlarge image]","key":"fig-add-vector","order":{"number":3,"section":[1,2,0,0,0,0,0]}}]}